Results.ReviewText: I bought this on offer instead of my usual Nescafe aand am so happy that I went straight out and bought 6 more jars.  The flavour is rich and smooth and its how coffee should taste the value for money is excellent, it is like having a barista grind it fresh and make it for you.
Results.Title: Gold is the new Black

Results.ReviewText: An excellent strong instant coffee.  It has a strong flavour in its own right which means there is no need to use extra coffee.  Using extra coffe with gold blend original for example it impairs the flavour.  Not as good as fresh ground, but the closest I have come across yet!
Results.Title: Nice strong coffee!

Results.ReviewText: I first tried this brand about 3 months ago more by accident than design - I actually picked up the wrong jar when shopping.  So glad I did though.  This has one of the best tastes of an instant coffee I've ever tried.  It may have been a mistake the first time, but not since
Results.Title: Perfect taste to wake up with

Results.ReviewText: Well it's my Husband that drinks the coffee and I have bought this one when it has been on a special offer and you know he said have you changed the coffee as I have only ever bought Nescafe so I said no and just showed him the jar and he just said cost it just tastes lovely.
Results.Title: GOLD Black

Results.ReviewText:
Myself and my family have been using Gold Blend for a long number of years. I feel that no one has successfully tried to usurp the No1 position that Gold Blend has, whether it be Gold Blend Black or any of its companions.
We will continue to use Gold Blend in its many forms.
Results.Title: excellent coffee

Results.ReviewText: loved the taste, the smell on opening the jar is fantastic every time. I tried it with cream, semi skimmed milk and coffee whitener, I even tried it black and every cup was delicious. My christmas treat will be a baileys cream in the cup while decorating the christmas tree
Results.Title: intense taste

Results.ReviewText: Like the taste but its no match for a fresh bean ground coffee, but that's OK this is a premium instant coffee, ideal for a quick on the go drink. I work in a lot of schools and their choise of instant coffee is horrific, so I always carry my own and this meets the demand.
Results.Title: Has potential for a quick brew

Results.ReviewText: I bought this about a week ago as it seemed appealing to me. I was right it has a rich coffee taste the way coffee should taste with no hint of bitterness that you can get with some coffees. The taste and smoothness lasts after you finish the cup making you want another.
Results.Title: Rich coffee

ClientResponses.Response: We're sad to hear you're not a fan of the changes we've made recently but thank you for letting us know!

Results.ReviewText: I have always bought Nescafé black gold coffe - even though not stocked by my usual supermarket!  Was happy to gone elsewhere to purchase this. Not any more - the “new” version is thin and lacking body. Very disappointed and am now searching for a suitable alternative.
Results.Title: Recipe change

Results.ReviewText: I HAVE BEEN A COFFEE LOVER ALL MY LIFE AND HAVE ALMOST TRIED  EVERY COFFEE MADE BUT NESCAFE BLACK IS REALLY A BUAUTIFUL TASTE AND ANY OTHERS DON,T EVEN COME CLOSE  AMAZING DRINK IN THE MORNING AND A  LOVELY SMELL IN THE MORNING TO BOOT HMMMMMMMM I CAN SMELL IT NOW ..
Results.Title: BLACK IS BEAUTIFUL

Results.ReviewText: An impulse buy a few days ago from my local supermarket. It's a lovely rich tasting coffee. Not too bitter but enough kick to wake me up in the morning. Very good value for money too! It tastes best black with a tiny amount of sugar in. And the smell is wonderful :-)
Results.Title: Lovely, rich and just what I need first thing!

Results.ReviewText: My normal coffee was out of stock and I'm so glad it was!! Never have I tasted an instant coffee with so much flavour, so much depth - and such an enticing aroma! Once I started drinking it in the office, the jar didn't last long - now it is our coffee of choice.
Results.Title: This can't be instant coffee!!

Results.ReviewText: The taste, the smell, the feeling from this coffee leaves me feeling, satisfied and ready to combat the day ahead of me. I feel like I'm treating myself to something indulgent with every cup. I have been converted to a nescafe coffee snob, in the best kind of way
Results.Title: Fell in love with coffee again

Results.ReviewText: I bought this last week and I love the new packaging as well as this coffee. When I opened the jar I was immediately reminded of freshly roasted coffee. The aroma was intoxicating. I used hot milk and the milk frother to give it a latte edge an it was divine
Results.Title: Smells like freshly roasted coffee beans

Results.ReviewText: I purchased this coffee, but did not expect it to be as good as it is, I like strong coffee as does my husband, and we were having to put more in with any other coffee, it just hit the right spot for us. and we shall continue buying it because we love it.x
Results.Title: like my men Strong.

Results.ReviewText: Love gold blend , I like a quite strong coffee this fits the bill,   has a fuller flavour, no aftertaste and really has the taste of a premium coffee.Tastes perfect either black or with milk. When you want a cup of coffee this is the one i would recommend.
Results.Title: Excellent taste

Results.ReviewText: I like my coffee black and strong on flavour, but detest the extreme bitter edge that comes with many strong coffees. Nescafe Black Gold is just perfect, strong and refreshing with a beautiful sharp and clean aftertaste, not a nasty bitter twang in sight.
Results.Title: Totally Refreshing

Results.ReviewText: Nescafe gold Black is a rich cup of coffee, so easily enjoyed on its own or with your favourite biscuit. I love the aroma when you twist the lid and open the jar. My favourite mug of the day is with breakfast, the smell, the taste the warmth, oh so good.
Results.Title: Very enjoyable cup of coffee

Results.ReviewText: I bought this instead of my usual variety and found that it is much better than that!  It makes delicious black coffee but a friend says that it was also great with milk. Strong but a good taste. No bitterness or aftertaste. I am definitely converted
Results.Title: Makes excellent black coffee

Results.ReviewText: Tried this last week and it has everything I want in a coffee. It's rich, smooth and just tastes wonderful! I now am starting to buy this in my weekly shop and I love the compliments that I get when I serve it to my friends, Happily recommend this.
Results.Title: My favourite

Results.ReviewText: We find this to be the most flavoursome instant coffee on the marketplace. The aroma is better than many filter coffees and on a blind test of flavour and aroma proved at least on a par with any more expensive coffees. I love it black and strong!!
Results.Title: Excellant Flavoursome Coffee

Results.ReviewText:
A well rounded strong roasted coffee . 
Strong full bodied taste, not over powering without a bitter after taste. 
Going through a re-education process to get the coffee to water dilution rate right for my taste, but when it’s right it zings.
Results.Title: Dark & Strong

Results.ReviewText: My Italian mother in law always made superb, strong, black coffee on the stove. Nescafé Black is the first coffee I have tasted since she passed away some years ago that matches what she brewed when we sat at her kitchen table. Great memories.
Results.Title: A tribute to my Italian mother in law

Results.ReviewText: I only drink black coffee without sugar and this stimulated my taste buds. The way I drink coffee nothing masks the flavour and so the true taste comes through. This is a delicious blend that ticks all my boxes. One for the true coffee lover.
Results.Title: Smooth,dark and rich

Results.ReviewText: I have used Gold  Blend for many years,and saw this newer version on offer in my local supermarket. I bought it, and really liked the flavour as it was so likecoffee from fresh ground beans.  Another brilliant addition to the Nescafe family.
Results.Title: Excellent flavour

Results.ReviewText: I discovered this coffee while I lived in Australia. I was so excited to discover it in the shops when I returned to live in the U.K. This coffee has a lovely full body, strong taste. I love the pungent aroma. Nescafé, you nailed it for me.
Results.Title: Full Bodied

Results.ReviewText: Thought I would give this a go, SO pleased I did, it's full bodied, not bitter and like it says on the label it has an intense flavour.  If you like your coffee strong, with an intense flavour but smooth  at the same time this is for you.
Results.Title: The Strong One

Results.ReviewText: I bought a jar of coffee in a rush at the supermarket thinking i would save money, I went back the following day to Buy Nescafe but kept the other make of coffee as a standby in case "anyone came to visit! friends and family excluded :-)
Results.Title: Not just coffee

Results.ReviewText: I bought this recently having enjoyed gold Blend in the past. This blend is great full of flavour a real pleasure to drink. Of course you could share with friends and family but why not be a little selfish and savour most of it yourself
Results.Title: Great flavour

Results.ReviewText: Bought this for the first time this week. I enjoy a strong blend first thing to give me some get up and go. This got me up and I went. Not bitter like some strong coffees. Smooth and flavoursome. Will definitely be on my shopping list.
Results.Title: Wake you up coffee

cb4d59cf-c48d-47ef-a943-50b2ae5d01ee.Description: A rich and full-bodied, premium coffee with strong toasted notes.
cb4d59cf-c48d-47ef-a943-50b2ae5d01ee.Name: NESCAFÉ GOLD Black

Results.Description: A well-rounded, smooth coffee with a rich aroma.
Results.Name: NESCAFÉ GOLD BLEND Instant Coffee
